hone were doomed to fail. Christensen argued that while Apple=E2=80=99s int=
egrated approach makes sense in the early days of a new market, over time, =
as the products=E2=80=99 components become commoditized, a more modular app=
roach wins out. When even modular products become =E2=80=9Cgood enough,=E2=
=80=9D the low-cost solution dominates the market.
